headline: How The Latest Price Target Is Rewriting The Story For Copart (CPRT)
summary: Copart’s latest price target has been updated, and that shift is prompting fresh questions about how the market currently views the stock. This change reflects a reassessment of the company’s outlook based only on the information available now, not on any assumed trend.
